stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> EnterSearchCriteria: Buyer opens search page

    EnterSearchCriteria --> ApplyFilters: Selects city, district, price range, type
    ApplyFilters --> SendRequest: Clicks Search

    SendRequest --> BackendValidation: GET /api/properties?filters
    BackendValidation --> BuildQuery: Parameters validated

    BuildQuery --> ExecuteSpatialQuery: SQL with PostGIS + JOINs
    ExecuteSpatialQuery --> ReturnResults: PostgreSQL returns rows

    ReturnResults --> CheckResults: Backend sends JSON response

    state HasResults <<choice>>
    CheckResults --> HasResults

    HasResults --> DisplayProperties: Results found
    HasResults --> ShowEmpty: No results

    DisplayProperties --> FetchImages: Frontend requests S3 media
    FetchImages --> RenderCards: Images loaded
    RenderCards --> [*]: Properties displayed on map + cards

    ShowEmpty --> [*]: "No properties found" message
